data.title: Memorial
data.meta_description: Order of St. Ignatius of Antioch C/O Zlata Ryan of the Antiochian located in Bolivar, PA
data.text:
With the spirits of the righteous made perfect, give rest to the soul of thy servants, 0 Saviour: and preserve them in that life of blessedness which is with thee, 0 thou who lovest mankind

May their Memory be Eternal!

His Eminence Metropolitan Philip Saliba + 1931-2014

Founder of The Order of St. Ignatius
